Lasagne is one of the world’s ultimate comfort foods. Meaty, cheesy and creamy, it has all the makings of a warming and delicious meal. And now, to make it even better people are adding yet another comforting food into the mix. Using bread, cooking masterminds are creating lasagne toasties. A mix of a cheese toasties and a plate of lasagne, make sure you make this delicious treat over the Easter weekend. The best part is that it is super easy to make and we love this recipe from TikTok account @foodmadesimple. Ingredients Method Do you have a story to share? Get in touch by emailing MetroLifestyleTeam@Metro.co.uk. MORE : Try this adorable hot cross bunnies recipe for Easter MORE : Three great recipes for rhubarb season – if you’re unsure what to make with the ingredient MORE : Kid-friendly recipes: Sweet potato macaroni that makes a great midweek meal